{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三章\"第二次决斗\"中，萧秋水在终南山以披风裹住费丹枫，使其中毒自毙。费家五人闻风而逃，萧秋水亲自埋葬费丹枫。随后萧秋水与陈见鬼、秦风八、疯女、阿水、刘友一行五人启程前往华山，途中被推举为\"神州结义\"盟首候选人。抵达华山后，在千尺幢天井隘口遭费鸦子伏击，萧秋水一剑刺杀费鸦子，费洪费晓推巨石暗算，萧秋水以深厚内力顶住巨石。封十五趁乱击伤阿水，萧秋水怒杀费洪费晓后与封十五决战，将其打落深崖。阿水伤重不治身亡，萧秋水将其水葬于瀑布深潭。一行人继续攀登华山，在老君犁沟遭遇费逸空截杀。费逸空以竹筒信号威胁，丐帮弟子以小网收走信号筒。萧秋水冲上蹬道，以剑斗铁犁，最终刺杀费逸空。此为萧秋水得八大高手相传后的第三次决斗，他已超越前人，形成自己的战斗风格。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "费丹枫",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你既是萧秋水，便活不下终南。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "text": "我不下终南。我上华山。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "费丹枫",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "把'天下英雄令'拿出来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "费丹枫",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你配吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我也去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我们一齐去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "疯女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我们本来赶到陕西来，是要接萧大哥过去，参加'神州结义'同盟盛会。我们皆一致认为，这领导非萧大哥莫属，故此才要萧大哥去一趟。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_feng_nv",
      "text": "是在哪一天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "三月十二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那天阴雨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "腥风血雨。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我会去的，但是我要先办完这件事再说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那未我们一起去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you",
      "speaker_name": "刘友",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "反正要回去，就一道回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_shui",
      "text": "一齐去闯荡也好，可别又摔交了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "萧大哥，如果你当上了'神州结义'的盟首，你有什么打算？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "没有打算。我是从一座山，走至另一座山。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是去打猎的，我爱这些山。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "不过一般的领袖都是先有所允诺，他出任后要做什么做什么的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "我不是领袖，我只是决斗者，或宁写诗、给画、沙场杀敌。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那你跟什么决斗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "text": "我跟自己决斗。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我不懂。要跟自己决斗……",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "text": "首先要择剑，排除万难、找到自己……只有天在上，更无山与齐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yazi",
      "speaker_name": "费鸦子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来的确定只是萧秋水和丐帮的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_fei_yazi",
      "text": "还有广东五虎的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yazi",
      "speaker_name": "费鸦子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不打紧。肯定上官族的人不在吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_fei_yazi",
      "text": "不在，他们的人，都出来了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yazi",
      "speaker_name": "费鸦子",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "你们二个，去通知山上，你们四个，留在这儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_shi_wu",
      "speaker_name": "封十五",
      "listener": "char_fei_yazi",
      "text": "几个小毛贼，还用这般阵仗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yazi",
      "speaker_name": "费鸦子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能杀丹枫的，多少有些能耐。不可以轻视。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yazi",
      "speaker_name": "费鸦子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "暖呀——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快跑！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "疯女",
      "listener": "char_a_shui",
      "text": "阿水小心——！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_shui",
      "text": "我已经替你报了仇了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我这一交，摔得好重……是我自己没有走好……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "在我们后面，跟有五个人，不知什么来路。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知是谁。",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好厉害。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "红衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连被打落悬崖的封十五，一共四个人，全死于萧秋水一人的剑下；萧秋水这个人，诚如老大所说，不可轻视。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yi_ren_hei",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧秋水也不简单，如果我所料不错，他在上面已发现了我们。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_liu_you",
      "text": "就葬此处了，刘女侠您看……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you",
      "speaker_name": "刘友",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 547,
      "line_end": 547
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yi_kong",
      "speaker_name": "费逸空",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你是萧秋水？",
      "tone": "傲慢",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yi_kong",
      "speaker_name": "费逸空",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我就是费逸空，我派去的人呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_fei_yi_kong",
      "text": "他们暗算我。已经给我杀了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yi_kong",
      "speaker_name": "费逸空",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你知道这是什么？这是信号。你杀了我儿子，我一燃引信，峰上的人便杀光你的朋友，哈哈哈……",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_fei_yi_kong",
      "text": "你去吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是第三关。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 687
    }
  ],
